reviewText: A heavy action with 2 pack here. "Wanted: Dead or Alive" stars Rutger Hauer ("Lady Hawk" and "Smallville") and rock legend Gene Simmons of KISS. Hauer is the tough as nails bounty hunter, and Simmons the global terrorist. In a turn of events, and government conspiracy, Hauer becomes the hunted and Simmons the hunter. "Death Before Dishonor" stars Fred Dryer ("Hunter") and Brian Keith ("Mountain Men"). Dryer is a hardcore Marine Sergeant who's embassy is attacked and his men taken hostage. These movies are full of beat 'em up, blow 'em action. I also specially recommend "Death Before Dishonor" for any who have served in the Corp. :)
